# NeuroSync — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in at least ONE AI provider key.

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  AI PROVIDER — pick one (or both; Groq is tried first if both are set)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── OPTION 1: Groq (RECOMMENDED — free, fast, no credit card required)
#
#   1. Go to https://console.groq.com
#   2. Sign up (free, no credit card)
#   3. Create an API key under "API Keys"
#   4. Paste it below
#
#   Free tier: 14,400 requests/day, 500,000 tokens/minute
#   Best model for NeuroSync: llama-3.3-70b-versatile
#
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here
# GROQ_MODEL=llama-3.3-70b-versatile   # default, change if needed
# Other free Groq models: mixtral-8x7b-32768, llama-3.1-8b-instant

# ── OPTION 2: Google Gemini (fallback)
#
#   1. Go to https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
#   2. Sign in with Google (free)
#   3. Click "Create API Key"
#
#   Free tier: 1,500 requests/day
#
# GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here
# GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.5-flash-lite

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  DATABASE
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# SQLite path (default: ./neurosync.db)
# DB_PATH=/data/neurosync.db

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  MULTILINGUAL — Bhashini (India GOI, optional)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Leave unset for English-only mode (safe default).
# Register at: https://bhashini.gov.in/ulca
#
# BHASHINI_API_KEY=your_bhashini_key
# BHASHINI_ENDPOINT=https://dhruva-api.bhashini.gov.in/services/inference/pipeline

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  EMAIL — Resend (optional, for sending reports by email)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Free tier: 3,000 emails/month, no credit card required
# Get key at: https://resend.com → Dashboard → API Keys
#
# RESEND_API_KEY=re_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
# NODE_ENV=production
# SESSION_SECRET=change-me-to-a-random-64-char-string
